{"tid":1220571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[兄弟爬山]社民連劉山青，請問你可以講少句當幫忙嗎？","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T16:33:57.000Z","uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b23ad35df2ef0395bf59515b28bbc4e00a12084","tid":1220571,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/user/529060/post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fuser%2F529060%2Fpost&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=9a8a77f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fuser%2F529060%2Fpost&h=e6ef06f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/user/529060/post</a><br />\n<br />\n暴民政治<br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動的教訓之一是出現暴民政治，先不說在旺角不斷與差佬衝突幫不了忙，在金鐘的第一周，已有示威者看到長期堵路有點問題。但當晚已有大批寫著「撤出是鬼」的標語，它堵塞了民主和理性的討論空間。今天的示威是相當和平、理性、非暴力的。至少，我從那些年青學生的臉上看不到暴戾之氣，但有一些人撬磚、築路障，若用武力或所謂勇武，示威者何能與荷槍實彈、訓練有素的防暴隊對抗呢？金鐘清場有力地說明築路障不但無用，而且有機會令已方的撤退受阻，百份百是自我高脹的幼稚行動。<br />\n<br />\n民陣<br />\n<br />\n民陣到夏愨道設大台，今天堵路不是它搞出來的，但它有一定使命。雨傘運動的教訓之二是運動需要糾察隊，不能讓一小部份人騎劫運動，無論它用民主還是什麼堂而皇之的藉口，運動也要反映參與者的多數意見。堆滿在金鐘聲援的青年人應討論其對擲磚和危險利器的意見。若能得出共識，便需要以群眾壓力說不。"},{"pid":"a4988f2aefbc15114c7829db8ad1268cb953ccec","tid":1220571,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e274387c7bd2214e9f2bfedd5bd65620c2f8c077","tid":1220571,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a790cf3add35fb616538c981e792547b729d752","tid":1220571,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiOCarU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiOCarU.jpg&h=d90f5bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trrDEkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrrDEkg.jpg&h=aebe4e70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9232d6a1d3c246fe583b7bb50a525ffcbbe69b16","tid":1220571,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064761&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=07cefebf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064761&h=fc0fafd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064761</a>"}]}